msgid "The available Actions"
msgstr ""

#: ../../_includes/_adminpanel/mta.rst:62
msgid "In the Postscreen Tuning section an **Action** is an operation made on an incoming e-mail whenever a test reaches a given threshold. That is, for example, when the incoming e-mail is marked as coming from a blacklisted source or contains some unwanted features."
