#: ../../_includes/_usage/wsc.rst:46
msgid "The most recent Chats or Groups will always appear at the top of the list. You can then filter the list if you search a particular Chat or Group."
msgstr ""

#: ../../_includes/_usage/wsc.rst:50
msgid "If you search and filter by user name, beside the single chat with him, you will find all the groups you are in, with that specific contact."
